"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 350px; height: 374px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Pemphigus foliaceus lesions exhibit erythema, scaling, and crusting. The face and scalp are often the initial sites of involvement.",
